Strategy Design Pattern
about the strategy design pattern so strategy design pattern is a part of a behavioral design pattern which will
allow us to Define different sets of algorithm for the different subclasses
and how we can use them interchangeably okay I know the definition was confusing
but let's try to understand with one of the examples here so let me take the example where I'm trying to Define one
